### ‚ú® New Features
- [`a785a62`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/a785a6295739cf74f31cca363dfced4dc5eb38f9) - add support for Android 5.0 *(PR #89 by @aliernfrog)*
- [`d07c411`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/d07c411d777a345182f366191f7d97a884a1d751) - **settings/about**: redesign credits & add libraries *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`5721c1f`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/5721c1fca56b96d1cc3b866e427000e815e0e50e) - predictive back gesture support *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`f5a97ac`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/f5a97ac01818f647f1d327553630809437dd6198) - **settings/about**: add option to copy debug info *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`3620cc4`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/3620cc44844fd3163376f1f0985c2d8a16b94d90) - **l10n**: partial Chinese translations & updates *(commit by @aliernfrog)*

### üêõ Bug Fixes
- [`b1abf36`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/b1abf3657880782ce9cd4b3e5c24ddb26672e4e8) - **l10n**: hide on Android 6 and below as it has no effect *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`4af780d`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/4af780dbb8b9c5cec681d3679fc07a3cd548c8c8) - navigation bar contrast on Android 6 *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`512f69d`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/512f69db8f30446d2760511acd66e203e982cf16) - **shizuku**: crash when processing +~1MB files *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`36b623b`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/36b623b05a54813419f4611ce91d27d3c176173e) - adjust navigation transitions *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`4fdf115`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/4fdf1152f75e1f4d310e8a853760deb843d2efa4) - **shizuku**: crash when writing +~1MB of data *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`71909a4`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/71909a42447162c508e9ad93e09ced6ee06c1783) - **shizuku**: create non-existing directories *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`061b3e3`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/061b3e3a3b16850aa88936a0abbb9b524e399a91) - **uri/to-path**: return as is if not an uri *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
